@startuml Sequence Diagram - Emergency Access
title Emergency Access Sequence Diagram

actor "First Responder" as FR
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Backend" as BE
participant "FHIR Server" as FHIR
participant "Audit DB" as Audit
participant "Patient Device" as Patient

FR -> App: Click "Search Patient"
App -> GW: POST /api/v1/patients/search
GW -> BE: Forward request
BE -> FHIR: Search Patient by name/DOB
FHIR --> BE: Patient data
BE --> GW: Patient summary
GW --> App: Patient found
App --> FR: Display patient

FR -> App: Click "View Emergency Data"
App -> GW: POST /api/v1/emergency/access
GW -> BE: Validate role & emergency enabled
BE -> FHIR: Get allergies, medications, contacts
FHIR --> BE: Emergency data
BE -> Audit: Log AuditEvent
Audit --> BE: Logged
BE --> GW: Emergency data
GW --> App: Data returned
App --> FR: Display data

BE -> Patient: Push notification (optional)
@enduml
